title: Eternal Kingdom 2022
description: Eternal Kingdom 2022 ManhuaOn a day like any other, the sky suddenly tore apart. Countless monsters rained from the sky. Relying on his innate Yin Yang Eyes, Yi Tian Xing survived the ‘Seven-Day Cataclysm’ with his younger sister and companions. After that, the millions of planets that appeared out of thin air started to merge with Earth to form a single gigantic planet. This marks the start of a new chapter on Earth – the Eternal Kingdom. 永恒国度 (2022)
